        <id>Cyanide.Cypher</id>
        <version>4.4.0</version>
        <title>Cyanide.Cypher</title>
        <authors>Nikolay Selyutin (HawkN113)</authors>
        <requireLicenseAcceptance>true</requireLicenseAcceptance>
        <description>Cypher query builder is a lightweight and intuitive C# library (fluent api) designed to construct Cypher queries programmatically for use with Neo4j or other compatible graph databases. It simplifies query creation by providing a fluent and type-safe API, allowing developers to focus on query logic rather than string concatenation.</description>
